---
title: Append-only job resolution decision lifecycle
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pending

    Pending --> MatchedExisting: sufficient evidence for existing identity
    Pending --> CreatedNew: no safe existing identity
    Pending --> Ambiguous: several plausible candidates
    Pending --> Rejected: observation is not a valid job opportunity
    Pending --> Ignored: accepted policy excludes processing

    MatchedExisting --> Superseded: corrected by later decision
    CreatedNew --> Superseded: corrected by later decision
    Ambiguous --> Superseded: review or new evidence creates decision
    Rejected --> Superseded: corrected by later decision
    Ignored --> Superseded: corrected by later decision

    MatchedExisting --> [*]
    CreatedNew --> [*]
    Ambiguous --> [*]
    Rejected --> [*]
    Ignored --> [*]
    Superseded --> [*]

    note right of Superseded
        Existing rows are never rewritten.
        A later JobResolution points back to
        the decision it supersedes.
    end note
